OL,3,CJustice Secretary dubs assisted dying
OL,4,CBill 'path to death on demand'
OL,6,FThe Justice Secretary has voiced
OL,7,Fserious concerns about a bill to
OL,8,Flegalise assisted dying ahead of a
OL,9,Fmajor vote next week, ITV News
OL,10,FPolitical Reporter Jasmine Cameron-
OL,11,FChileshe reports
OL,13,FThe state should "never offer death as
OL,14,Fa service", the Justice Secretary has
OL,15,Fsaid, in a strongly worded
OL,16,Fintervention over the assisted dying
OL,17,FBill ahead of a historic Commons vote
OL,18,Fnext week.
