OL,7,Fthe pressure the elderly, vulnerable,
OL,8,Fsick or disabled may place upon
OL,9,Fthemselves".
OL,11,FThe intervention appears to be at odds
OL,12,Fwith guidance set out by Cabinet
OL,13,FSecretary Simon Case last month that
OL,14,Fministers should remain neutral on the
OL,15,Fissue and avoid taking part in public
OL,16,Fdebate.
